implements com.opensymphony.xwork2.Preparable, org.apache.struts2.interceptor.SessionAware, org.apache.struts2.interceptor.ServletResponseAware
    The action for executing saved issue filters (Tree and TQL) The filter is not opened for editing before execute (not instantly modified) but may contain parameters
